cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CE, cs.RO 

The paper proposes a learning agent for a thermostat using reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with decision-making under uncertainty, which is a common theme in control systems (cs.SY) and control engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper proposes an auto-encoder, which is a common technique in robotics (cs.RO) for feature extraction and dimensionality reduction.
